---
const embed = `<script src="https://unpkg.com/@portable-inventory/widget-sdk"></script>

<portable-inventory
  api-key="pk_live_..."
  mode="scan"
  theme-primary="#6366f1">
</portable-inventory>`;

const points = [
  "Web component o classe JS, in un iframe sandboxato",
  "Temizzabile: colori, raggio, font e lingua",
  "QR dinamici, singoli o in batch fino a 100",
  "Chiavi API con permessi granulari e allow-list CORS",
];
---

<section id="widget" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
  <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400">Integra ovunque</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-50 sm:text-4xl">
        Il magazzino, dentro qualsiasi sito
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">
        Incorpora Varasto con una riga di codice. Il tuo team — o i tuoi clienti — scansiona un QR e
        aggiorna le giacenze senza mai entrare nel gestionale. E la chiave API non finisce mai
        nell'URL.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
        {
          points.map((p) => (
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-zinc-300">
              <span class="inline-flex h-5 w-5 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/15 text-indigo-400">
                <svg class="h-3 w-3" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M16.7 5.3a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.4l-7.5 7.5a1 1 0 0 1-1.4 0L3.3 9.7a1 1 0 1 1 1.4-1.4l3.1 3.1 6.8-6.8a1 1 0 0 1 1.4 0Z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"
                  />
                </svg>
              </span>
              {p}
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-white/[0.08] bg-zinc-900 shadow-xl shadow-black/40">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-white/[0.06] px-4 py-2.5">
        <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/70"></span>
        <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500/70"></span>
        <span class="h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/70"></span>
        <span class="ml-2 font-mono text-[11px] text-zinc-600">embed.html</span>
      </div>
      <pre class="overflow-x-auto p-5 text-[12.5px] leading-relaxed"><code class="font-mono text-zinc-300">{embed}</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
